Description: Aptura Shell desktop integration
 Installs Aptura Shell, desktop launchers, and utility hooks.
 The default desktop uses Aptura's own Wayland shell profile with labwc,
 waybar, wofi, Aptura contextual branding, practical workstation tools,
 firmware visibility, power controls, local journey/context tooling, and
 a local system health check. KDE Plasma remains available as a fallback
 session and application base.
